<br>
a) Dress nicely<br>
<br>
b) Invite you Dad or Mom along to court<br>
<br>
c) Apologize for your friend's actions <br>
<br>
d) Practice your 'puppy dog' eyes<br>
<br>
If you follow the above steps it should land you a PBJ(probation before judgement) and some court costs and a lowered fine.<br>
<br>
I had a citation for reckless Driving, 68mph in a 25 mph zone, $270 fine and 5 points, got it reduced to $100 and 2 points with my clean driving record and a vow from my pops that i had been severely punished for my transgression.<br>
<br>
Hope this helps!<br>
