<br>
28 mph is over the limit in a parking lot. the speed limit is 10 or 15 depending.<br>
<br>
the cop does not need to be stationary for him to radar you. so im sure he didnt pull 28 outta his ass.<br>
<br>
yes you can fight it and win easy. some cops dont show. and if this is your first offense and you act like a normal human being to the judge/magistrate, then its really up to him to dismiss it.<br>
<br>
ive gotten 2 tickets and fought both and won both times. you basically just have to show initiative and show that you are sorry and it wont happen again.<br>
<br>
good luck. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=177099"> Xanter </a><br>
